data.description: Come Enjoy Easy Living in this Well Maintained 4 Bedroom Ranch with a Master Suite in an AWESOME Neighborhood, Outdoor Oasis with Inground Pool, screened in porch overlooking it, Fenced in Yard, patio for grilling next to the pool.  Inside Has Plenty Of Room For Entertaining With a HUGE Dining Room, Comfortable Family Room Next To The Fire Place!!!  All 1/3 Of a Mile to Stillwater Schools.
